{"tid":862000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國潮興大象皮下脂肪做成血珠 大量大象被活生生剝皮殘殺","createTime":"2018-10-14T14:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T19:18:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":315,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5456f91e2dbd13c5eba8725c8a2762cda42a25","tid":862000,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2180000/2182911/ele_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2180000%2F2182911%2Fele_600.jpg&h=235ecc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸大象慘遭剝皮，走私中國製成血色念珠鏈及胃藥。（Elephant Family圖片）<br />\n<br />\n緬甸的亞洲象向都受偷獵者剥走獠牙的威脅，但近年偷獵者竟看上了大象的皮膚，轉售到中國製成「胃藥」、護膚品及血紅色的念珠手鏈等等，導致緬甸野生大象全家慘遭「屠殺」，甚至未斷氣就被活生生地剥皮的慘況，令人髮指！<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司（ABC）日前進入緬甸採訪亞洲象情況，在仰光工作的大象保育員Aung Myo Chit每次得知發生偷獵事件，便會立即駕數小時車前往偷獵大象的現場，但他看見的是令人反胃的情景：<br />\n<br />\n即使你已經離屍體有1英里遠，仍能聞到那陣惡臭，大象全身的皮都被剥去，河水染滿了血！<br />\n世界自然基金會（WWF）緬甸主任Christy Williams指出，他們調查過中緬邊界的市場，發現近年大象皮的交易急速上升，當中有9成顧客來自中國，象皮除直接經邊界，亦經泰國和老撾走私到中國。<br />\n<br />\n偷獵者使用土製槍枝向大象射出毒箭，兩日後劇毒會滲透全身每吋皮膚，大象經歷緩慢而痛苦的死亡，然後商人會把含有毒素的大象皮風乾，再搗成粉末，作為「胃藥」和護膚品出售。<br />\n<br />\n 緬甸大象以往多因象牙遭盜獵，但近年獵人目標轉向象皮，令雌性大象也成為獵物之一，甚為殘忍。（Elephant Family圖片）<br />\n緬甸大象以往多因象牙遭盜獵，但近年獵人目標轉向象皮，令雌性大象也成為獵物之一，甚為殘忍。（Elephant Family圖片）<br />\n<br />\n此外，2014年起內地開始流行一款血色念珠手鏈，念珠由硬化的大象皮下脂肪製成，血紅色正正來自大象的血，因此偷獵者要在大象倒下就立即剥皮，免得血液流走褪色，使得大象甚至未斷氣就被活生生地剥皮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2180000/2182911/Triple_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2180000%2F2182911%2FTriple_600.jpg&h=49ea2fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 大象的皮下脂肪能夠製成血珠，作為首飾配戴。（Elephant Family圖片）<br />\n大象的皮下脂肪能夠製成血珠，作為首飾配戴。（Elephant Family圖片）<br />\n<br />\n現時緬甸有6000隻馴養的大象，在伐木業工作，而野生大象則有2000隻，Williams指，如果再不制止捕獵大象，牠們很可能在2030年前就在緬甸徹底消失。"},{"pid":"74f8fc011b5113640632eca699dcfe21f636ef21","tid":862000,"uid":61625,"like":351,"dislike":2,"score":349,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母係咪有病啊啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02c55ea5d1f3b747b5dd18df7c2245796d93c5f","tid":862000,"uid":51546,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85972f9331e0ffb0cc9a4e459146a47d4595ab97","tid":862000,"uid":216528,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"仆街支那終蟈人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805f41ee109b68fce6c21ebca33b7a7fd7cd7ac3","tid":862000,"uid":54373,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2180000/2182911/01_thumb_20181014_kin_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2180000%2F2182911%2F01_thumb_20181014_kin_1024.jpg&h=4fffbded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇見到痛<br />\n唔知支那賣幾錢粒珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d2a60267c4a0d1c30c0faf17735fb2e34a9c02","tid":862000,"uid":187076,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EG458t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EG458t.jpg&h=d466aa29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fff99eef953bb9ae09b6bfc3c4a4aee89ac5371b","tid":862000,"uid":33481,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:17:07.000Z","msg":